{"tid":1426063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視斥年輕人淪亂港頭目扯線公仔","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:52:20.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"27af12eeeee8e3da393975532652c9789ca7f729","tid":1426063,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565101105_7N-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565101105_7N-1280w.jpg&h=ab345ffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地官媒繼續炮轟香港日漸升級的示威衝擊。央視今晚發文批評，「一系列亂港事件中出現了一些年輕的面孔」，他們「喊打喊殺沖在前，但實際上，他們只不過是一些提線木偶」。文章還引用《大公報》刊登、署名為港區全國政協委員、香港新時代發展智庫主席屠海鳴的評論，同聲批評「亂港頭目李柱銘、陳方安生、黎智英」等人的子女「無一上街遊行」，而將「別人家的孩子」當作「政治燃料」及「用來引發摩擦、造成衝突的『炮灰崽』」，「用心何其險惡！」<br />\n<br />\n央視又質問，「亂港派大佬」既然視「民主、自由、人權」如陽光與空氣，一刻不能缺少，又「既然視『違法達義』為正義之舉，『舉義』就在當下，亂港頭目為甚麼不把當『英雄』的好機會留給自己的子女呢？」央視認為，「亂港頭目心裡非常清楚，自己所做的是缺德事、違法事、骯髒事，不能讓自己的子女參與」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，央視在今晚的《新聞聯播》中批評，「香港的愈演愈烈的暴力活動已無關修例爭議，少數暴徒的犯罪行徑劣跡斑斑，少數亂港分子囂張狂妄，竟敢挑戰國家尊嚴。這些跳樑小丑的險惡居心，就是企圖綁架全港市民，癱瘓香港政府，進而公然挑戰國家主權和中央政府權威，明目張膽地進行政治要脅」。<br />\n<br />\n央視還斥，「少數跳樑小丑蚍蜉撼樹，不自量力&hellip;&hellip;躲得過初一，躲不了十五！少數亂港暴徒所欠的債遲早是要還的」，而「我們堅信，有偉大祖國作為堅強後盾，有14億中國人的鼎力支持，香港一定能回歸理性、回歸安寧」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%96%A5%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B7%AA%E4%BA%82%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%AD%E7%9B%AE%E6%89%AF%E7%B7%9A%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94-183624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%2596%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%2589%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BB%2594-183624&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=5ec3743b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%96%A5%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B7%AA%E4%BA%82%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%AD%E7%9B%AE%E6%89%AF%E7%B7%9A%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94-183624</a>"},{"pid":"dad932838659690d4d566958bc9b8a272dc124d0","tid":1426063,"uid":222190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySzErtG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySzErtG.png&h=cd937bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/083711_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F083711_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=18aec7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/083712_0dccc94b7190dc5fb97749cfc3216e2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F083712_0dccc94b7190dc5fb97749cfc3216e2b.png&h=2f54971b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/083714_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F083714_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=bdba104c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/083716_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F083716_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png&h=313e7cf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0df667c5409d1d73fc384e51f3a12c601f35100e","tid":1426063,"uid":56015,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"有頭目你仲唔捉撚咗佢咩? 中國都on 99"},{"pid":"ddba4ca2668bff4d96e3ee0a9375240d7c703d4f","tid"